title: Good Omens | Sinners - [Aziraphale + Crowley]
author: Sleuthette
comment: “Our hearts are too ruthless to break” while Crowley is saying ‘aziraphale...’ like a breath of fresh air after he thought he died wAS JUST UNNECESSARY TEARS

TO THE WORLD

BUT MY WORLD IS ONLY YOU

[screams calmly]
I have a playlist on spotify called “soft to be strong” for these 2 and this song is on there and this is basically what plays in my head when I listen to that underrated song, and I am LOSING MY MIND over how beautifully perfectly this is edited, thank you so much for doing the Lord’s work, wow wow wow
I never knew I NEEDED a Good Omens FMV to the song Sinners until I saw it, but goddamn am I glad you made it because I needed it. Thanks for making this lovely video.
THE SONG- Oh my God the placement to the scenes and the Lyrics!!! That’s them, the Sinners who did everything right and are together till their dying days.
